instruction: Create a data visualization to compare the age of cats and dogs
output: A bar chart can be used to compare the age of cats and dogs. The x-axis will show different age groups such as 0-1 years, 1-2 years, 2-3 years, etc. The y-axis will show percent of cats and percent of dogs in each age group. The bars will represent the percentages of cats and dogs in each age group. The chart will demonstrate the relative age ranges of cats and dogs.
